{"word":"καταίρω","slug":"καταίρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταίρω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ᾰρῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to come down, make a swoop</i>, of birds, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; of persons, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of ships, <i>to put into port, put in</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}